                        <div class="row py-3">
                            <p class="primary-text">In this Financial Modeling course, we will use the Harley-Davidson Case Study to learn how to build up a financial model from scratch, beginning with obtaining SEC filings and progressing through building the financial model in Excel. We will also examine the revenue build-up model, income statement, cash flow, and balance sheet.</p>
